to tell Molly?

16:55.542 --> 16:57.792
<i>♪ Jingle bells, jingle bells... ♪</i>

16:57.875 --> 17:01.834
Any minute, kiddo. You'll get your wish.

17:01.917 --> 17:06.040
Snow so clean and white,
you could wash clothes in it.

17:07.750 --> 17:09.416
Oh, I can't wait!

17:09.500 --> 17:13.458
Santa, oh, Santa.

17:19.500 --> 17:21.208
Come on, let us in!

17:24.583 --> 17:27.250
Louie, what's the idea, locking us out?

17:28.000 --> 17:32.041
This is no Louie. This is Santa Claus.

17:32.125 --> 17:34.625
[all laughing]

17:36.667 --> 17:40.333
Hey, now, wait a minute--
Where did you get those threads?

17:59.500 --> 18:01.625
Now, hold on here.

18:01.709 --> 18:03.917
I can explain.

18:19.291 --> 18:22.625
Molly, no, wait! I can--oh.

18:22.709 --> 18:25.208
What did you guys do that for?

18:35.291 --> 18:37.166
[crying]

18:54.542 --> 18:57.583
A lie. This was all a lie.

19:28.792 --> 19:32.041
[Rebecca Cunningham] Molly!

19:32.125 --> 19:34.959
