19:36.041 --> 19:39.375
Now what am I going
to give Mom for Christmas?

20:10.000 --> 20:11.625
Hee hee!

20:13.083 --> 20:14.583
Hee hee!

20:28.250 --> 20:31.125
Molly!

20:35.375 --> 20:38.792
Molly, honey, are you all right?

20:39.000 --> 20:42.792
What are you doing here without your coat?

20:42.875 --> 20:45.542
You can't catch cold on Christmas.

20:47.500 --> 20:50.041
Molly, what is it?

20:50.500 --> 20:53.875
Mommy, I saw him.

20:55.875 --> 21:00.000
Baloo, do you see...

21:01.083 --> 21:02.250
Uh-huh.

21:04.834 --> 21:07.208
Hey, what you guys looking at?

21:26.750 --> 21:28.458
Crazy.

21:28.667 --> 21:30.792
Is that what I think it is?

21:34.709 --> 21:36.458
Wow!

21:43.959 --> 21:45.667
Hee hee hee!

21:45.750 --> 21:47.709
Hee hee hee!

21:47.792 --> 21:50.959
Hey, I finally made it work.

21:55.083 --> 21:56.792
How'd you do it?

21:56.875 --> 21:58.125
I didn't.

21:58.208 --> 21:59.208
Then who?

21:59.375 --> 22:00.834
Louie, my man,

22:01.000 --> 22:04.000
you wouldn't believe me if I told you.

22:06.166 --> 22:07.500
I would.

22:08.291 --> 22:10.667
Merry Christmas, Mommy.

